Just clone this in ~/config or something, and run ./install in it.

You should put your personal git configuration (like your name and email)
in ~/.gitconfig.local.

Don't forget to run ./install again when you update.

If VIM complains about weird characters, add the following to your .vimrc
set encoding=utf-8  " The encoding displayed.
set fileencoding=utf-8  " The encoding written to file.
